@startuml mebaysan_Modern-Data-Architecture

actor "DevOps Engineer" as DevOps
participant "Docker Compose" as DockerCompose
participant "Airbyte Container" as Airbyte
participant "PostgreSQL Container" as Postgres
participant "DBT Container" as DBT
participant "Superset Container" as Superset
participant "Nginx Container" as Nginx
participant "pgAdmin Container" as pgAdmin

DevOps -> DockerCompose : 1. Run docker-compose up
activate DockerCompose

DockerCompose -> Airbyte : 2. Start Airbyte
activate Airbyte
DockerCompose -> Postgres : 3. Start PostgreSQL
activate Postgres
DockerCompose -> DBT : 4. Start DBT
activate DBT
DockerCompose -> Superset : 5. Start Superset
activate Superset
DockerCompose -> Nginx : 6. Start Nginx
activate Nginx
DockerCompose -> pgAdmin : 7. Start pgAdmin
activate pgAdmin

DockerCompose --> DevOps : 8. All containers started

DevOps -> Airbyte : 9. Configure data source
Airbyte -> Postgres : 10. Load data

DevOps -> DBT : 11. Run transformations
DBT -> Postgres : 12. Transform data

DevOps -> Superset : 13. Set up dashboards
Superset -> Postgres : 14. Query data

DevOps -> pgAdmin : 15. Manage database
pgAdmin -> Postgres : 16. Administer

Nginx -> pgAdmin : 17. Proxy requests

@enduml